<subSubSection pageId="19" pageNumber="20" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="19.[151,1436,1534,2030]" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1933,1958]" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">Remarks.</emphasis>
Given that the original description of this species is incomplete and its redescription made by 
<bibRefCitation author="Vercammen-Grandjean" box="[151,649,1969,1994]" pageId="19" pageNumber="20" refString="Vercammen-Grandjean, P. H. &amp; Langston, R. L. (1976) The chigger mites of the World (Acarina: Trombiculidae et Leeuwenhoekiidae). III. Leptotrombidium complex. George Williams Hooper Foundation, University of California, San Francisco, 1061 pp." type="book" year="1976">
Vercammen-Grandjean and Langston (
<number box="[583,641,1969,1994]" pageId="19" pageNumber="20" value="1976.0">1976</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
is hardly accessible, here we provide figures and measurements of our material (Figs. 
<number box="[321,394,2006,2030]" pageId="19" pageNumber="20" value="13.0" valueMax="14.0" valueMin="12.0">12–14</number>
, 
<tableCitation box="[405,491,2005,2030]" captionStart="TABLE 4" captionStartId="20.[151,236,152,175]" captionTargetBox="[159,1181,202,1350]" captionTargetPageId="20" captionText="TABLE 4. Standard measurements of Whartonacarus chaetosus." httpUri="http://table.plazi.org/id/08C46660FF9EFF9E49FDFF76FCC7FF02" pageId="19" pageNumber="20" tableUuid="08C46660FF9EFF9E49FDFF76FCC7FF02">
Table 
<number box="[474,491,2006,2030]" pageId="19" pageNumber="20" value="4.0">4</number>
</tableCitation>
).
</paragraph>
